    • 方法详细资料

      • getPanelsFor

        java.util.List<VehicleCommAdapterPanel> getPanelsFor(@Nonnull
                                                     VehicleCommAdapterDescription description,
                                                     @Nonnull
                                                     TCSObjectReference<Vehicle> vehicle,
                                                     @Nonnull
                                                     VehicleProcessModelTO processModel)
        Returns a list of VehicleCommAdapterPanels.
        参数:
        description - The description to create panels for.
        vehicle - The vehicle to create panels for.
        processModel - The current state of the process model a panel may want to initialize its components with.
        返回:
        A list of comm adapter panels, or an empty list, if this factory cannot provide panels for the given description.
